nt<br />\n嚟緊月尾會去英國想開埋N26<br />\n但係聽講用英國地址開係俾英鎊戶口而唔係歐羅戶口<br />\n係咪真?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n用英國mail forward地址開左 係出英鎊戶口<br />\n而家等緊張卡<br />\nmonzo都整左 又係等緊卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"一樣，有邊間可以入歐羅/人仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"歐羅/美金"},{"pid":"e615e82ae141e0b60dd8d26419a78b84e0a6181b","tid":1569202,"uid":312916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25170b6407be73d7989bc8b95a5a6c120b53dce2","tid":1569202,"uid":21134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989bf0d20f1a4e4190f5e7c73db31b72d01d79b5","tid":1569202,"uid":312916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"307f5ff5d1208a13bd7936683befc3a144412eb8","tid":1569202,"uid":21134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"純想走資 平時係香港用返張卡/Apple pay消費<br />\n開一間夠做？<br />\n見N26張卡好鬼靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢幾間係咪全部要搵forwarder收信再轉寄返香港？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"歐洲以英國最易搵到mail forwarding services.<br />\n<br />\nN26 張實體卡真係好靚 ，但以匯率換算來說，平時用Monzo, Starling，Revolut, TransferWise較佳。<br />\n<br />\n暫時只有瑞士dukascopy bank 可接受香港地址開戶，<br />\n<br />\nMonzo, Starling 一定要有英國residential address,<br />\n<br />\nN26 要有歐盟/EEA 或英國residential 地址 （跟地址發出EURO 或GBP account),<br />\n<br />\nRevolut and Transferwise, 你要用歐盟/EEA 或英國地址，才可開到account 及debit card.<br />\n(Transferwise 如果你用香港地址，只有匯款功能，沒有account及沒有debit card)<br />\n<br />\n另外TransferWise debit card近日進軍美國，澳洲，紐西蘭；<br />\nMonzo, N26也進軍了美國。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"就咁睇好似transferwise較好<br />\n但剛上網睇了啲blog 話transferwise入金出金較煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:46:34.000Z","msg":"TransferWise Borderless Account, send ＄出去一定要收手續費;<br />\n<br />\n另外由外面send ＄入TransferWise Borderless Account, 有時好快入帳（幾分鐘內）；<br />\n間中則會extra security check, 要2-5天才入帳。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然TransferWise Borderless Account好處，是你會有齊英、德、美、澳洲、紐西蘭5個之銀行戶口號碼：<br />\n<br />\n英國 - TransferWise UK (Partner bank: Barclays)<br />\n德國 - Handelsbank DE(即Germany）<br />\n美國 - Community Federal Savings Bank<br />\n澳洲 - Moneytech Payments P/L (CRU)<br />\n紐西蘭 -Bank of New Zealand (Branch: TransferWise)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有TransferWise Debit Card (由UK發出的）暫時未能加入Apple Pay Wallet.<br />\n<br />\nRevolut, Monzo, N26等均可加入Apple Pay Wallet."},{"pid":"a6392ed7c80b2583d2e8c60957da2974ae69509d","tid":1569202,"uid":312916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc262e98c06c2d8e9f352a8229fb554f41c4ad0","tid":1569202,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74c1b97ac5185c81178890c70e2489815b7a2955","tid":1569202,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a03ff6dbbf8022c1d53e3aee9f55477c167d96cf","tid":1569202,"uid":146986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n用英國mail forward地址開左 係出英鎊戶口<br />\n而家等緊張卡<br />\nmonzo都整左 又係等緊卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:30:03.000Z","msg":"一樣，有邊間可以入歐羅/人仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"歐羅/美金"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"TransferWise 和 Revolut 也可有英鎊、歐羅、美金 （甚至是澳元、紐元、日元等）<br />\n<br />\nRevolut 好處是工作日（星期一至五）各貨幣兌換價較靚，但只有英鎊和歐羅的銀行戶口號碼 （其他貨幣沒有當地銀行戶口號碼）<br />\n<br />\nTransferWise則有5大貨幣的當地銀行戶口號碼<br />\n（你會有齊英國、美國、德國、澳洲、紐西蘭5國當地銀行戶口號碼）<br />\n但各貨幣互相兌換價較Revolut無咁靚。"},{"pid":"d300372e24a8c6ec634bf5dcfafed9a943715dcb","tid":1569202,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"Revolut 好似好多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gi